title: #215 - Big Jay Oakerson & ME
description: Comedian Big Jay Oakerson & I hang in the Mancave and talk about getting our ears peirced for the first time, comics who like to giggle vs. comics who don't, his first tattoo, our love for Amy Schumer, Kevin Hart, Daniel Tosh, Dave Attell, Todd Glass, and our week working on the Goddamn Comedy Jam.
